                    <comment id="13051147" author="yseeley@gmail.com" created="Fri, 17 Jun 2011 16:50:40 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Good idea... +1 for a power factor above 1.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                    <comment id="13051151" author="mikemccand" created="Fri, 17 Jun 2011 17:00:13 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Simple patch, adding setReclaimDeletesWeight to TMP, and defaulting it to 2.0.  I also fixed LTC.newTieredMergePolicy to randomly set this...&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                    <comment id="13051173" author="thetaphi" created="Fri, 17 Jun 2011 17:30:59 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Great idea, I was thinking about that when I wrote the reply about no need to optimize in java-user!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
